sorcer.util

Class LibraryPathHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
      • java.util.AbstractSet<String>
        • sorcer.util.LibraryPathHelper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<String>, Collection<String>, Set<String>

    public class LibraryPathHelper
extends AbstractSet<String>
    LibraryPathHelper implements a Set<String> synchronized with system property java.library.path. each change is immediately reflected in the Java runtime. All Set operations are synchronized.
    Author:
    Rafał Krupiński
